column1: 1 name: Sample name without spaces or symbols.
column2: 2 lat: latitude used to calculate the muon contributions (DD).
column3: 3 site_elv: elevation of the sample above sea level (m).
column4: 4 Isotope (used to calculate the muon contributions )
column5: 5 base_level: elevation of the fluvial or glacial surface at the site area (m).
column7: 7 dApparent_years: External uncertainty of the apparent age (a).
